HEADWORD: Monogamic
<hw>Mon`o*gam"ic</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Monogamous</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Pertaining to, or
involving, monogamy.</def>⟦br⟧
