<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the
<ord>Monogamia</ord>; having a simple flower with united
anthers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monogamist</ent>⟦br⟧
